          "id": "f4",
          "description": "The second 'Application runtime orchestration' entry adds a parenthetical that contradicts the first entry and partially overlaps the in-scope carve-out stated in <authority>",
          "source_section": "<scope>"
        }
      ],
      "redesign_guidance": "Collapse to one entry for each exclusion. For runtime orchestration, use a single line: 'Application runtime orchestration outside this tool's board-review loop' to preserve the in-scope carve-out without contradiction."
